{"hfbf19e0ag8324g481bg8e2bgd15156845c4e": ["A child's future, taken before our eyes.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "04a35397-2a2f-43ab-aeb5-bfafdb199117"], "h18e74effgb68dg4598gb938g135c2045effe": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "04a35397-2a2f-43ab-aeb5-bfafdb199117"], "h53db1d4fg5e87g4ccegba4cgc4b2965e70c1": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "04a35397-2a2f-43ab-aeb5-bfafdb199117"], "hb65b1969g1af7g4c20g9ca5g717a4fbc17bd": ["Another dead refugee. What a sorry bunch of souls.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "04a35397-2a2f-43ab-aeb5-bfafdb199117"], "hd33ccdf8g3d04g4714g8a0bgf74082549e7e": ["  | I want to know your opinion on X. (Shadowheart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "04a35397-2a2f-43ab-aeb5-bfafdb199117"], "h4fa5d606g01a5g40f4gaba0g1673250fe6c1": ["The elf is nothing if not merciless. The girl paid a high price for her crime.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "04a35397-2a2f-43ab-aeb5-bfafdb199117"], "h31a92bb6g7a3cg4b86gb6e5gfc4864bdd7fa": ["  | I want to know your opinion on X. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "04a35397-2a2f-43ab-aeb5-bfafdb199117"], "h64acb587gf473g4059g888dg62a7e32cf190": ["  | I want to know your opinion on X. (Gale Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "04a35397-2a2f-43ab-aeb5-bfafdb199117"], "heac2079bgbafbg4f63gbb23g8a2889268ceb": ["The snake killed that girl in front of everyone. Is this grove worth a dead child?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "04a35397-2a2f-43ab-aeb5-bfafdb199117"], "h51a80d33g1c0eg4891g8665g9b49f146edb5": ["An unfortunate tragedy. Kagha couldn't have foreseen it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "87dfb689-b207-47db-b658-fbf9c321e5c7"], "h04b0cfc2g59d8g4fb3gabaaga8859124b75b": ["A logical outcome. Kagha identified a defect in her grove, and the serpent removed it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "87dfb689-b207-47db-b658-fbf9c321e5c7"], "h91d08fbcg92a1g478bg96aagac0ba2d0ec6f": ["The girl bolted and the snake reacted - it was a sorry accident, nothing more.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "87dfb689-b207-47db-b658-fbf9c321e5c7"], "h1465edf9gbe67g4b42g8d4cg5d667b08c7ce": ["| I want option A (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "87dfb689-b207-47db-b658-fbf9c321e5c7"], "ha5090b41g9ee4g4c91gab65g1e677bfb275c": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "87dfb689-b207-47db-b658-fbf9c321e5c7"], "hb1c0d24fga71fg4e7dg8b48gc322d048f97d": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "87dfb689-b207-47db-b658-fbf9c321e5c7"], "h90d21f84gaf22g4a27g953bg660e926c7d44": ["| I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "87dfb689-b207-47db-b658-fbf9c321e5c7"], "h5091b966g432bg4c77gaf5cg1cef3ff9b611": ["| I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "87dfb689-b207-47db-b658-fbf9c321e5c7"], "h642e84b7gdd96g4036g8b70gcbcb71e17936": ["It was bound to happen. The druids and tieflings were already on edge.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "87dfb689-b207-47db-b658-fbf9c321e5c7"], "h0f849c33g8b16g4369g81f4gb10b1a30694e": ["An unfortunate tragedy, yes. Kagha couldn't have foreseen it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "8f483cee-f5b1-416e-b1da-6e82e02f31be"], "h3a98f167g699fg4198gb10fg8469f36b675e": ["A logical outcome. Kagha identified a defect in her grove, and the serpent removed it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "8f483cee-f5b1-416e-b1da-6e82e02f31be"], "h50fec156g2e33g4423ga5bdg1063006f7185": ["Precisely - it was a sorry accident, nothing more.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "8f483cee-f5b1-416e-b1da-6e82e02f31be"], "hea95fce8gff3eg4fcdg9d7bg90d0141480cf": ["| I agree. I want option A (ShadowHeart Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "8f483cee-f5b1-416e-b1da-6e82e02f31be"], "h1254b2c5gb428g4b61gb767g7e65ecfd7ac7": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "8f483cee-f5b1-416e-b1da-6e82e02f31be"], "hc4afd140g0352g48edg9327g55e43c507fa1": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_ShadowDruid_RD_KidDied.html", "8f483cee-f5b1-4